Khalil – Cold Blanket Super talented artiste, Khalil formerly known as Ghetto P releases a brand new single and video titled “Cold Blanket”. ‘Cold Blanket‘ is a sweet melodious feel good vibe and it is housed under his new extended play tagged ‘Grown‘. The EP is scheduled for release before the end of the year. The song was produced by young producer, Wordz and the video was directed by WG Films. Check ’em out below! AUDIO DOWNLOAD GET IT ON DIGITAL STORES The post VIDEO: Khalil – Cold Blanket appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay